        did not discuss test or examination findings. [ <TIMEX TYPE="DATE">12</TIMEX> ] In
        addition, <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">blacks</ENAMEX> were less likely than <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">whites</ENAMEX> to be
        satisfied with the care provided during their most recent
        hospitalization or ambulatory care visits. [ <TIMEX TYPE="DATE">13</TIMEX> ] One
