        than uninsured <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">patients</ENAMEX> of the same PSI <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">class</ENAMEX> (OR <NUMEX TYPE="MONEY">0.4685</NUMEX>,
        <NUMEX TYPE="PERCENT">95%</NUMEX>CI <NUMEX TYPE="CARDINAL">0.1923</NUMEX>-<NUMEX TYPE="CARDINAL">0.6981</NUMEX>). Numerous studies have shown that
        uninsured <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">persons</ENAMEX> have greater difficulty accessing
