        <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">et al</ENAMEX> in their study compared hospitalized <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">patients</ENAMEX> and
        found that after adjusting for diagnosis related <ENAMEX TYPE="ORG_DESC">group</ENAMEX> case
