        frequently have their need for hospitalization reassessed
        by a senior <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">physician</ENAMEX>. [ <TIMEX TYPE="DATE">21</TIMEX> ] The decision to hospitalize
        is not necessarily a commitment to long-term inpatient care
        but rather a decision that certain <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">patients</ENAMEX> should be
        closely observed until it is clear that therapy can be
        safely continued out of the <ENAMEX TYPE="ORG_DESC">hospital</ENAMEX>. Even in institutions
