        <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">day of ED</ENAMEX> evaluation (<TIMEX TYPE="DATE">weekdays</TIMEX> versus <TIMEX TYPE="DATE">weekends</TIMEX>) were
        <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">associated</ENAMEX> with differences in hospitalization rates of low
