        Although <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">Fine</ENAMEX> and <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">colleagues</ENAMEX> state that low-risk
        <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">patients</ENAMEX> should be considered as <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">candidates</ENAMEX> for outpatient
